{"lemma":"وَضَحُ","slug":"وَضَحُ","root":"#.ض.ح","root_slug":"_-ض-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ض-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42017","","n42020"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be clearly visible"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become clearly visible"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make clear, to clarify; to elucidate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"broad light, brightness"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/wa.dˤa.ħa/","/wadˤ.dˤa.ħa/","/wa.dˤaħ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42017","headword_ar":"وَضَحَ","root":"wDH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDiHu","text_ar":"يَضِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuDuwHN","text_ar":"وُضُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiHapN","text_ar":"ضِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaHapN","text_ar":"ضَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) the last with fet-hah because the guttural letter; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"At~DH","text_ar":"اتّضح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AwDH","text_ar":"اوضح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twD~H","text_ar":"توضّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an affair,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K, and a thing,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'N","text_ar":"شَىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appeared; became apparent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plainly apparent, overt, conspicuous, manifest, notorious, plain, obvious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evident;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became clear, unobscured, exposed to view, displayed, laid open, disclosed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncovered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(language)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was perspicuous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(The Lexicons, passim.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maloku AlT~ar~iyqi","text_ar":"مَلْكُ الطَّرِّيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twD~H","text_ar":"توضّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The middle of the road became plainly apparent, obvious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conspicuous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano A^ayona waDaHa Alr~aAkibu","text_ar":"مَنْ اَيْنَ وَضَحَ الرَّاكِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as AZ says, or, as others say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn Ayn AwDH","text_ar":"من اين اوضح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whence did the rider make his appearance?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) Or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHa Alr~aAkibu","text_ar":"وَضَحَ الرَّاكِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the rider came forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn Ayn A^awoDaHta","text_ar":"من اين اَوْضَحتَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whence hast thou come forth?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S,) and [in like manner one says]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn Ayn badaA waDaHuka","text_ar":"من اين بَدَا وَضَحُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHati AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"وَضَحَتِ الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAll~abani","text_ar":"بِاللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alomaEat","text_ar":"اَلْمَعَت"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDiHa","text_ar":"وَضِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [a verb of which the inf. n. is explained in the Msb by the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drn","text_ar":"درن"},{"kind":"text","text":": if this be not a mistake of a copyist, it app. signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was dirty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was dirtied, soiled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"besmeared"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","L","K","ISd","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n42020","headword_ar":"وَضَحٌ","root":"wDH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Light, and whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) of anything: (TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness of daybreak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dawn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the moon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and its light."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuwmuwA mina AlwaDaHi A_ilaY AlwaDaHi","text_ar":"صُومُوا مِنَ الوَضَحِ اـِلَى الوَضَحِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fast ye from new moon to new moon."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, from a trad.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Leprosy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraSN","text_ar":"بَرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) It is sometimes used in this sense, metonymically. (S.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mark in a horse differing in colour from the generality of his coat."},{"kind":"text","text":"You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlfarasi waDaHN","text_ar":"بِالفَرَسِ وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the horse is such a mark."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A blaze,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white mark on a horse's forehead"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHojiylN","text_ar":"تَحْجِيلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the legs of a horse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) And also applied to other varieties of colour. (L.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frasN *uw A^awoDaAHK","text_ar":"فرَسٌ ذُو اَوْضَاحٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse having a blaze and what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHjyl","text_ar":"تحجيل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whiteness of the hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoary, hair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b9-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) thought by ISd to be so called because of its whiteness: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk that has not been mixed with water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is just drawn."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zhr","text_ar":"زهر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Aboo-Dhueyb says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"Eaq~awoA bisahomK falamo ya$oEuro bihi A^aHadN\n                      \n                     \n                        vum~a A@sotafaw^uwA waqaAluwAHab~a*aA AlwaDaHu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They shot an arrow towards the sky, and no one knew of it: then they returned, and said, An excellent thing is milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: meaning, we would rather have milk than the blood of him who has killed our companion: they preferred that camels should be given them in compensation. (L.) [See also 2, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EqY","text_ar":"عقى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sound, whole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perfect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver coin, of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diroham","text_ar":"دِرْهَم"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirohamN waDaHN","text_ar":"دِرْهَمٌ وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A clean, white dirhem:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoDaAHN","text_ar":"اَوْضَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main part and middle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a road; the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a road"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"along which one travels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman's ornament"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of silver:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, K:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of stones;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Meshárik;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of silverstones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Towsheeh:) so called because of its whiteness: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoDaAHN","text_ar":"اَوْضَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoDaAHN","text_ar":"اَوْضَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of woman's ornament"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of whole"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver coins such as are called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraAhim","text_ar":"دَرَاهِم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and (according to some, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an anklet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaloxaAlN","text_ar":"خَلْخَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) ―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN AlT~ariyfapi","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ الطَّرِيفَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, but the latter word is there written;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tryqp","text_ar":"طريقة"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Small portions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts, of herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what he has become white thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoDaAHN","text_ar":"اَوْضَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoDaAHN mino kalaA_K","text_ar":"اَوْضَاحٌ مِنْ كَلَاـٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat of herbage that has become white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As:) Az says, I have mostly heard the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with respect to herbage, applied to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~iyaAn SayofiY~","text_ar":"صِلِّيَان صَيْفِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is not a year old and has not become black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and on another occasion he says, that it is the remains of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaliY~","text_ar":"حَلِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~iyaAn","text_ar":"صِلِّيَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"only. (L.) ―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whiteness predominating over other colours"},{"kind":"text","text":"in sheep or goats,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overspreading generally the whole body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoDaAHN","text_ar":"اَوْضَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the breast and back and face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) you say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu tawoDyHN","text_ar":"لَهُ تَوْضيحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino A^ayona badaA waDaHuka","text_ar":"مِنْ اَيْنَ بَدَا وَضَحُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1. ―         -b16-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHu Alqadami","text_ar":"وَضَحُ القَدَمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whiteness of the hollow of the sole of the foot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","L","K","AHn","As","T"]}]}}